WEBVTT

00:00.141 --> 00:03.943
So on this side, as you can see, hundreds and hundreds of refugees from Ukraine.

00:04.498 --> 00:08.375
This lane is free, so we're going to try to go into Ukraine.

00:13.213 --> 00:14.414
On the Ukrainian side,...

00:14.594 --> 00:18.091
...the imagery, more like a refugee crisis as we know it.

00:19.863 --> 00:22.955
The traffic queues over 20 miles long, we're told.

00:26.898 --> 00:30.194
Of the over half a million Ukrainian refugees now on the move,...

00:30.633 --> 00:35.835
...Poland has, as of today, recorded over 280,000 entries.

00:36.284 --> 00:38.284
Slovakia, 30,000.

00:40.810 --> 00:43.755
Charities told us that the vast majority of people here...

00:44.069 --> 00:47.233
...are being picked up by friends and relatives on the other side.

